<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsHidonRace.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1621" title="EkolimpicChampsHidonRace" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsHidonRace.jpg" alt="" width="299" height="179" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">כתב חידה</span></strong></p>
